## Lookup

Provide exactly one of:

| argument | behavior |
|---|---|
| `id` | Direct fetch by integer tag ID. |
| `name` | Exact-match search by name. Must resolve to exactly one tag, otherwise an error is raised. |

## Returned values

| attribute | description |
|---|---|
| `id` | Tag ID (`int64`). |
| `name` | Tag name. |
| `color` | Tag color. A free-form string (1-16 characters); there is no fixed palette or enum. |
| `description` | Tag description (may be null). |
| `resource_ids` | Set of network-resource IDs (`int64`) currently assigned this tag. |
| `resource_count` | Number of resources assigned this tag. When looked up by `id`, this equals the size of `resource_ids`. |
| `created_at` | Creation timestamp (RFC 3339). |
| `updated_at` | Last-update timestamp (RFC 3339). |
